{"tid":1635323,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗其實都幾唔識計數","createTime":"2019-10-07T13:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:11:28.000Z","uid":172613,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"97b8bde71c793c71ae045ee79a6715016eedae7a","tid":1635323,"uid":172613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:01:55.000Z","msg":"雖然現實上冇乜可能，但係都容許小弟打下飛機<br />\n班狗依家係到擁護政權，冇錯係鎮壓示威者方面一定係會成功<br />\n但係睇翻國際形勢其實示威者方係有幾大嘅優勢，尤其係人權法案<br />\n如果班狗肯回頭是岸加入反政府陣營嘅話，就算到最後真係政府贏都好，起碼歷史上唔使比人叫做狗，可以洗白<br />\n但係依家如果繼續打壓示威者嘅話，無論最後邊一方贏都好，班狗其實都會面臨清算，淪為condom<br />\n如果mon post狗睇到嘅話，老土咁講句，自己諗下做狗定係做人啦"},{"pid":"6a3dcf42fa3cb4f61c5b107ab714460e9d8f849f","tid":1635323,"uid":212961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:02:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n<br />\n聽日係反蒙面法之後嘅第一個工作日<br />\n求下大家<br />\n和勇一家，合力三罷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要做到被罷工嘅情況！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4b42094de17e426db6ef364a96915bc19e5372","tid":1635323,"uid":302944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"仲想班狗會回頭是岸?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機會已經比左幾次 都冇一個出黎篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做得狗既 一早已經冇左個腦"},{"pid":"676c488427958e109819568263df5a0af668cf2f","tid":1635323,"uid":172613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e4b42094de17e426db6ef364a96915bc19e5372","tid":1635323,"uid":302944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"仲想班狗會回頭是岸?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機會已經比左幾次 都冇一個出黎篤灰<